                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.6363/2425: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morrow</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-11-17T18:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 17, 1927—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 8: 58 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>412. The Supreme Court rendered decision today which is reported to hold articles
                    14 and 15 of petroleum law unconstitutional. Will report fully when copy of
                    decision is obtained.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morrow</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
